@startuml
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam backgroundColor #F9F9F9
skinparam shadowing false

package "crates" {
    [rusty-claude-cli] as cli
    [tools] as tools
    [runtime] as runtime
    [api] as api
}

package "Layers" {
    [UI Layer] as ui_layer
    [Agent Core] as agent_core
    [Tools Library] as tools_lib
    [API Client] as api_client
}

package "External" {
    [User] as user
    [LLM Provider] as llm_provider
}

' Привязка крейтов к слоям
cli --> ui_layer
runtime --> agent_core
tools --> tools_lib
api --> api_client

' Взаимодействие между слоями
user <--> cli : interacts with (terminal)
cli --> runtime : sends prompts\nreceives events
runtime --> tools : executes tools
runtime --> api : sends requests\nreceives responses
api --> llm_provider : HTTP API

cli .[#3C89F7].> tools : uses for actions
runtime .[#3C89F7].> tools : executes built-in\nfunctions

note right of cli
  Terminal REPL + one-shot
  Builds runtime from TOML
  Renders transcript
end note

note right of runtime
  Manages session state\n  Tool routing\n  Permission enforcement\n  LLM orchestration
end note

note right of tools
  Contains ~40 built-in\n  tools (bash, read_file,\n  WebSearch, Agent, etc.)
end note

note right of api
  Abstracts LLM provider\n  type = anthropic |\n  openai (OpenRouter,\n  qwen, DeepSeek, Ollama)
end note

@enduml